   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>Steps to reproduce
1. Visit <a href="http://openhatch.org/search/">http://openhatch.org/search/</a>
2. Click the voice search function
3. The text returned by the voice search will have the voice search appended to 
the search field with the text textual search. The field should have been 
cleared.</pre>
